Class Rfc4515BaseListener

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.github.pms1.ldap.Rfc4515BaseListener
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Rfc4515Listener, org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.ParseTreeListener

    public class Rfc4515BaseListener
extends Object
implements Rfc4515Listener
    This class provides an empty implementation of Rfc4515Listener, which can be extended to create a listener which only needs to handle a subset of the available methods.
